In regards to the difference in quality, This appears to be much crisper than previous releases. 

Many wont be able to tell a difference in quality when viewing on a handheld device with a 2 inch screen, But for those of us that view these handheld releases on say a ps3 or an ipod to tv via an a/v adapter this is where the difference can be seen. As I stated the video is much crisper and not as grainy as previous releases I have come across when viewing on TV. 

Thanks for all your hard work and trying to tweak your uploads to give  us the best quality possible.
